name: OFFICE OF DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL, Petitioner v. Gregory D. KEENEY, Respondent
name_abbreviation: Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Keeney

parties: OFFICE OF DISCIPLINARY COUNSEL, Petitioner v. Gregory D. KEENEY, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 18th day of June, 1998, upon consideration of the Report and Recommendations of the Disciplinary Board dated May 1,1998, it is hereby
ORDERED that GREGORY D. KEENEY be subjected to PUBLIC CENSURE by the Supreme Court.
It is further ORDERED that respondent shall pay costs to the Disciplinary Board pursuant to Rule 208(g), Pa.R.D.E.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:
